Package: causatr
Title: Unified Causal Effect Estimation for Methodological Triangulation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Lorenzo", "Fabbri", , "lorenzo.fabbri92sm@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3031-322X"))
Description: Estimates causal effects via g-computation, inverse probability
    weighting, and matching for methodological triangulation. Primary engine
    is the parametric g-formula and iterated conditional expectation (ICE)
    g-computation with empirical sandwich variance estimation. Integrates
    WeightIt for IPW and MatchIt for matching. Supports binary, continuous,
    categorical, and multivariate treatments; static, dynamic, and modified
    treatment interventions; continuous, binary, censored, and
    competing-risk outcomes; survey weights and clustered data.
